title: Can't find the network my pixel is locked
content:
Hello, 
I bought a pixel 3 from online auction site which came with box and everything but it is locked to a network and i cannot find which one. 
The phone is not blacklisted. 
However the Google support is shockingly useless they wouldnt help at all when i provide them with imei number they wont even let me know who is the carrier.
The phone is in UK.

Many thanks

Mario
